  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >1986, somewhere in the Rocky Mountains. After spending the last of your money on booze and a cheap motel room, you're awoken by a loud crash. Feeling psychosis kicking in, you crack your paws ready to fight through weird enemies and creatures!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Features:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >FPS game play inspired by PO'ED, Doom, and Unreal!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Six totally rad levels to explore.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Like, seriously strange secrets to find.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Ten bodacious weapons!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Locate notes to find out what happened.</p></li></ul>",
